We are a backpacker hostel located in a residential HDB (Housing and Development Board) estate in Singapore; Bukit Merah. This unique setup is one of its kind in SG and by staying with us, you get to experience the authentic Singapore lifestyle!

We offer travelers no frills budget accommodation and we are within 30 mins bus ride away to most key tourist attractions. We are also walkable to Tiong Bahru; a hip hotspot for cafes, wall murals, filled with old school charm.

Stay with us today!
